  "time_ut": 1658212579,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba3\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Electricity bill increases",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Chairman of Public Utility Commission Janaka Ratnayake has said that the electricity tariff will be increased from the beginning of August.",
        "Janaka Ratnayake also said that although the Electricity Board has demanded a 130 percent tariff hike, the tariff hike will be implemented by giving concessions to low electricity consumers. (R)"
      ],
